          "LessonTitle": "Lesson 2: Neural Network Components",
          "Content": "In this lesson, we will dive deeper into the components of a neural network. We will discuss neurons, weights, biases, and the role they play in the functioning of a neural network. We will also explore the concept of forward propagation and how it helps in making predictions."
        }
      ]
    },
