          "LessonTitle": "Lesson 1: Origins of Neural Networks",
          "Content": "In this lesson, we will explore the history and origins of neural networks. We will discuss the early inspirations for neural networks, such as the human brain, and how researchers started developing computational models based on these inspirations. We will also touch upon the challenges faced in the early days of neural network research."
        },
        {
          "LessonTitle": "Lesson 2: Evolution of Neural Networks",
          "Content": "In this lesson, we will trace the evolution of neural networks over time. We will discuss the key milestones and breakthroughs that have shaped the field of neural networks. We will also explore the impact of advancements in hardware, algorithms, and data availability on the development of neural networks."
